{"id": 2871, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在什么时候会对“时间”特别斤斤计较？", "description": "一个当代迷思：明明自己处处都在“节约”时间，但省下来的时间……好像也没做什么。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 2652, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190401162117Oj6DP4nscmr0QatL.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-02T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 337152, "content": "deadline，下班后的“补偿”时间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1524165}, {"id": 337920, "content": "怎么还不下班？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601892}, {"id": 337153, "content": "我说学习，你们信吗？33岁突然发现自己什么都没有，只有学习为自己增值！", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1617267}, {"id": 338177, "content": "等公车   想着另外一辆我的这辆回早点来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623180}, {"id": 337154, "content": "路上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618806}, {"id": 337666, "content": "上课的时候总期盼早点下课，恨不得时间再快点，看手机看手表看来看去才过了几分钟，放假了，好不容易放个小长假，立下了N个flag，一转眼，已经开学了，可惜计划本上的任务一个还没完成，时间啥时候过的～绝望啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629238}, {"id": 339202, "content": "考试的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373131}, {"id": 337155, "content": "每次要学习的时候都是争分夺秒，赶快坐下打开书、拿起笔……转了几下笔然后拿起来手机🙂", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626557}, {"id": 337156, "content": "食堂排长队打饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450211}, {"id": 337157, "content": "排队的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429344}, {"id": 337158, "content": "堵车的时间如梭，开会的时间漫长", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 582462}, {"id": 337160, "content": "不注重时间，会被社会遗忘！太专注时间，会被时间定格！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 639402}, {"id": 337672, "content": "被插队的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1581043}, {"id": 337161, "content": "下课不想去食堂排队，等人少了再去吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1442711}, {"id": 337162, "content": "人到中年", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460843}, {"id": 337164, "content": "开车夹三儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1142495}, {"id": 337165, "content": "马上要交稿了，我却才开始动笔", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626695}, {"id": 337166, "content": "工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626703}, {"id": 338446, "content": "上课，一节课的时候怎么这么长", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633869}, {"id": 337169, "content": "游戏匹配的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626718}, {"id": 337425, "content": "期末复习的时候！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1628073}, {"id": 337170, "content": "考研", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1175318}, {"id": 337171, "content": "如果要走路掐着点没出发就会打滴(。)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1576910}, {"id": 337172, "content": "等待", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626736}, {"id": 337173, "content": "等待", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626736}, {"id": 339989, "content": "起迟了。Deadline前夕。跟不喜欢的人出门。规定时间背单词。看剧二倍速。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1598126}, {"id": 343573, "content": "上课的时候有人提问没用的问题的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602649}, {"id": 337175, "content": "做爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1418382}, {"id": 337176, "content": "体能测试QAQ", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425155}, {"id": 336922, "content": "下班的地铁上，还有两三站的时候就开始点外卖", "image": null, "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 336923, "content": "等公交，估摸着“几点几分去刚好赶上”再掐点出门", "image": null, "praise_count": 100, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 336924, "content": "坐地铁，上车前会先算一下“哪个门下车出站最快”", "image": null, "praise_count": 63, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 337180, "content": "早上买早饭排队的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615380}, {"id": 336925, "content": "看视频先关注时长，再决定要不要看完", "image": null, "praise_count": 177, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 337181, "content": "在考试前复习，总觉得时间不够。😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626757}, {"id": 337182, "content": "老师拖堂的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626769}, {"id": 337183, "content": "等人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601869}, {"id": 337184, "content": "作为学生党，对时间特别斤斤计较的当然是上下课时间和早起的时间。哈哈哈  我猜肯定有不少人感同身受。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626778}, {"id": 337185, "content": "亲人要离开的时候，时间就像抓不住的沙子", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626798}, {"id": 337441, "content": "再喊完室友起床后，室友让我等他们整理完一起去上课", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123397}, {"id": 338209, "content": "约定好的时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002334}, {"id": 336930, "content": "等电梯，虽然只要几分钟，还是觉得“怎么来这么慢”", "image": null, "praise_count": 444, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 337186, "content": "5分钟有多长取决于你在厕所里面还是厕所外面", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1404966}, {"id": 337187, "content": "赖床", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1625342}, {"id": 337189, "content": "数学考试", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623598}, {"id": 337191, "content": "做饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1542908}, {"id": 337192, "content": "每天放学回到家 感觉没写多少作业也没怎么看手机 就要十二点了......", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626862}, {"id": 337193, "content": "写作业和看书时，还有在感兴趣的的事时，感觉时光飞逝。在等绿灯，等厕所，等人时，时光缓缓。主动参与时时光是快的，这时，时间带我们领略相对与我们的光速。在等待时，又理解了在宇宙中的光速", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626868}, {"id": 337194, "content": "写论文..", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1622270}, {"id": 337450, "content": "共事的时候，因为别人的低效率，我要多做很多工作，搞得我很累，耽误我的时间，谋我财害我命。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1627920}]}